Mage Lapis: I was just dedicated to studying magic! Why

Mage Relm: Listening to your words... makes me feel

Mage Lapis: Perhaps I was bought by a noble! If that's the

Mage Lapis: Even without being told, I will do it! Now,

Mage Relm: Th-There's no need to say such things! Now, let's
